Typography: deals with styles and appeaeance with text 

<div class="mat-display-4">This is display 4</div>
<div class="mat-display-3">This is display 3</div>
<div class="mat-display-2">This is display 2</div>
<div class="mat-display-1">This is display 1</div>


<div class="mat-headline">This is headline for h1</div>
<div class="mat-title">This is display h2</div>
<div class="mat-subheading-2">This is subheadingfor h3</div>
<div class="mat-subheading-1">This is subheading for h4</div>


<div class="mat-body-1">This is body text</div>
<div class="mat-body-2">This is bold body text</div>
<div class="mat-caption">This is caption text</div>


 <div class="mat-typography">
     <h1>Heading H1</h1>
     <h2>Heading H2</h2>
     <h3>Heading H3</h3>
     <h4>Heading H4</h4>
 </div>